            <title>[LU-11526] Support 64MB I/O RPC</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11526</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the new SFA, the blcok driver allows 32MB max_hw_sector_kb from vOSS (SFA embeded stack) to SFA below.   Lustre should have bump up maxim IO size to 32MB RPC. We need maximum drive efficiency at least benchmark and small number of client configuration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
